<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Project Update</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2196F3;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .update-box {
      background-color: #e3f2fd;
      border: 1px solid #bbdefb;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .update-type {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1976D2;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .update-details {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #2196F3;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #1976D2;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Project Update: {{projectName}}</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    
    <p>There has been an update in the project you're collaborating on.</p>
    
    <div class="update-box">
      <div class="update-type">
        {{updateType}}
      </div>
      
      <div class="update-details">
        {{{updateDetails}}}
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{projectUrl}}" class="button">View Project</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>You can also access the project directly at:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all;">{{projectUrl}}</p>
    
    <p><small>You're receiving this email because you're a collaborator on {{projectName}}.</small></p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>To manage your notification preferences, visit your account settings.</p>
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Our Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
